gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 111, 76ers 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the 76ers, 111-105. Nikola Jokic recorded 26 points, 16 rebounds and seven assists for the Nuggets, while Jamal Murray added 23 points and a season-high six 3PM in the victory. Paul Reed tallied a career-high 30 points, along with a season-high 13 rebounds for the 76ers in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 32-15 on the season, while the 76ers fall to 29-15.
